trans-unit.source: Provides data for the events in the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart"></xref> control that change the position of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder data for hendelser i den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart"> </xref> kontrolltypen endre plasseringen av merknaden.

trans-unit.source: The AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs class is used for the two annotation-positioning events, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged>, in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs brukes for to plasseringen av merknaden hendelser, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged>i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs.Annotation%2A> property gets the annotation object that is being positioned.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs.Annotation%2A>egenskapen henter merknad-objektet som er plassert.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs.Annotation%2A>

trans-unit.source: This class also contains properties that retrieve the new location, width, height and anchor location of the annotation that is repositioned.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen inneholder også egenskapene som henter ny plassering, bredde og høyde og ankeret plasseringen av merknaden er ny posisjon.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs>klassen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The Annotation property allows the developer to set <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation> properties during the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> events of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen merknad gjør det mulig for utviklere å angi <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation>Egenskaper under den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged>hendelser i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation>
